becomeAHost.aBetterExperience.descriptio: 报告是自动且实时的，所以每个人都可以随时看到最新的预算。项目可以更直接地管理其资金，而资金赞助者可以确保一切依赖其政策进行。
becomeAHost.benefit.combineFunding.descr: Collectives可以通过各种渠道寻求支持，同时在一个预算中跟踪一切。 集资、信用卡付款和活动票销售是内置的 而且你可以很容易地将任何其他方式的资金贷记入正确的预算。
becomeAHost.benefit.easyExpense.descript: 受款人通过平台提交开支，附有相关的发票和收据，来提取资金。通过你的管理员控制面板查看和批准费用 ，你可以 通过银行转账或贝宝付款支付费用。
becomeAHost.benefit.inDepthReports.descr: 无需花时间为资助者创建报告 — 它是随时自动和透明地记录的。 此外，你将每月收到一份包含所有交易和文档的综合报告！
becomeAHost.benefit.keepTrack.descriptio: 为你需要的项目创建Collective，只需几次点击，无需额外费用。 每个Collective都有自己的筹资、预算追踪和社区参与的网页。 收到的付款将添加到正确的Collective余额。不需要电子表格！
becomeAHost.caseStudies.allforclimate-co: 为你的地方气候公正小组提供资金赞助， 我们是一个共用的行政后台，以便地方团体能够集中精力采取行动。
becomeAHost.caseStudies.opensource: 我们为数千个公开来源项目提供资金和法律基础设施。 我们是分布式合作世界与会计和发票世界之间的 API。
becomeAHost.caseStudies.socialchangenest: 我们目前支持了超过 150 个互助小组迅速开展工作，并为他们提供了财务托管支持。
becomeAHost.caseStudies.wwcode: 每当我们开始一个新的聚会章节时，我们都会将其与Open Collective 配对，这样他们就有办法在我们的保护下筹集资金。
becomeAHost.description: Open Collective 是为了简化你的流程、减少间接费用和提高透明度而设计的。其允许你的组织在更少的时间内为更多的项目筹集和管理资金。
becomeAHost.entity: 任何拥有银行账户的实体
becomeAHost.entity.description: 运营多个项目，并希望使用Open Collective平台功能进行透明的预算跟踪的人，可以将收入流、费用支付管理和社区参与相结合。
becomeAHost.fiscalSponsorshipService.des: 在其选定的地理或工业领域。
becomeAHost.grantMakers.description: 那些想要减少未纳入项目和非正式倡议的障碍，同时确保强有力的监督的人。
becomeAHost.increaseCapacity.description: Open Collective 使你能够在更少的时间内为更多的项目提供更多服务。大量的交易将不会使你过度疲劳，因为平台使大部分工作自动化，并且还会收集任何你设置的资金持有费。
becomeAHost.joinUsSection.subtitle: Open Collective使财政赞助在阳光下进行。受赠者和项目参与者会喜欢我们服务的便捷，并且你会喜欢上费用管理成本的大量降低。
becomeAHost.networks.description: 那些希望在经营一个共同的法律实体（如聚会和社会运动）的同时实现当地筹款的人。
becomeAHost.nonprofits.description: 那些希望使推进其任务领域的非法人项目能够在其保护伞下获得赠款和捐款的人。
becomeAHost.reduceOverhead.description: 当你为多个项目或小组管理资金时，很容易被复杂的电子表格和无数的电子邮件困扰。Open Collective自动化预算跟踪、报告、费用处理和支付，使你的工作更加轻松。
becomeAHost.title: 资金赞助从未如此简单。
becomeAHost.whatAreTheBenefits: 与我们一起托管有什么优势？
becomeAHost.whatAreTheBenefits.descripti: 接受捐赠和赞助，庆祝支持者增长，支付费用，并让大家随时了解最新情况——都在同一个地方。
becomeASponsor.backYourStack.description: 发现你的开源依赖并向他们提供支持。
becomeASponsor.bulkPayments.description: 你可以向财政主管发送一笔付款，在平台上向你的组织贷记，而不是用信用卡向每个集体付款。然后，你可以使用这笔余额为任意数量的集体提供资金。
becomeASponsor.giftOfGiving.description: 为员工、客户、招聘候选人、活动参与者创建礼品卡，以便你的社区能够支持他们关心的集体，而你的组织是公认的资助者。
becomeASponsor.giftOfGiving.title: 赠送礼物
becomeASponsor.invoiceReceipts.descripti: 向未注册的社区、运动和项目提供资金可能是一场会计上的恶梦。Open Collective通过记录每笔交易的文档解决这个问题。
becomeASponsor.monthlyInvoice: 此外，在平台上获取一张月度综合贡献的发票会让你的会计感谢你！
becomeASponsor.moreFeatures.description: 发现我们的功能的可能性。
becomeASponsor.moreFeatures.title: 更多功能
becomeASponsor.paperWork.description: 你想支持的集体的财务托管方是一个成熟的法律实体，可以与你的供应商系统和采购订单流程打交道，并满足文件要求，如税表和签署协议。
becomeASponsor.reporting.description: 除了每月的报告外，集体还可以定期发布关于其进展和支持获得的回响，还可以随时查看他们的预算——就像是自己写的报告一样！
becomeASponsor.supportCommunities: 支持社区，帮助他们成长。
becomeASponsor.supportCommunities.descri: Open Collective 平台使财政赞助实体能够接纳非公司团体，为它们提供一个你可以接触的法律结构。
becomeASponsor.supportProjects.descripti: 加入这些伟大的创始人和赞助者并支持他们令人惊讶的倡议。透明的贡献和全部你所需要的文书工具，汇总在一处。

fiscalHosting.crowdFunding.description: Seeking a place to hold the money and a way to offer accountability to their backers.
fiscalHosting.description: Think of your community, project, or initiative as a plant, and a fiscal host as a lovingly tended garden. The host maintains an environment where your unique bush, vine, or tree can get watered, grow, and bloom.
fiscalHosting.distributeCollaboration.de: Like an open source software project, which isn’t owned by anyone and wants resources held in common.
fiscalHosting.feature.acceptAndSpendFund: You can often get approved very quickly, even instantly, ready to receive and disburse funds and get operational. Compared with traditional fiscal sponsorship or setting up your own entity, activating with a fiscal host is super streamlined.
fiscalHosting.feature.automaticReporting: No need to spend hours creating reports for funders. The Open Collective platform has automated quantitative reporting built in. Just sent the funder a link to your page! There are great tools for qualitative reporting too, like posting blogs and newsletters, which also serve to keep your wider community engaged and up to date.
fiscalHosting.feature.networkingAndSolid: A fiscal host is by definition a community of projects with something in common. They can provide services to their community as a whole, and enable connections between projects. Whether it’s about joining budgets or joining voices, join a host that’s more than the sum of its parts.
fiscalHosting.feature.organizeFinance: 在一个地方解决所有财务问题
fiscalHosting.feature.organizeFinance.de: No more messy spreadsheets! Income from credit card transactions, bank transfers, PayPal, even ticket sales, grants, and sponsorships are all tracked automatically in one transparent budget. With a robust yet user-friendly system for submitting and approving expenses, tracking outgoing funds is a breeze, too.
fiscalHosting.feature.organizeFinance.ta: 你的所有财务信息集于一处
fiscalHosting.feature.sustainabilityDesi: If your project doesn’t have an expiration date, neither should your funding. A standard crowdfunding campaign is over once it’s over. A single grant is spent once it’s spent. But fiscal hosting helps you combine different income streams and form ongoing relationships with funders.
fiscalHosting.fees.description: Fiscal hosts often charge a fee for the service they provide. Some hosts keep fees low and offer a lightweight service, while others have higher fees and provide more support. Some fiscal hosts don’t charge fees at all.
